{"tid":782923,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[第四次] 日語入門體驗班","createTime":"2018-08-17T07:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T13:38:11.000Z","uid":175564,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a804b9e5c3c77a5939ad3ca57eede9cd7f9e18","tid":782923,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打好,又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有日文班比大家JOIN, 都係FOR 初學者,大約只係N5程度<br />\n會教D 基本50音,簡單旅遊用語,同少少句形結構等<br />\n起我底都知道我地之前都搞過好多次活動,非搵食,係健康嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我地今次個報名方法有D特別, 我地整左個叫Finterest嘅網站,日後我地會陸續擺D活動上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finterest.link/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinterest.link%2F&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9acf3a39\" target=\"_blank\">https://finterest.link/</a><br />\n<br />\n巴絲打可以用tg or email 申請AC, 然後報名。<br />\n最好用電腦或者iphone 申請, 用Android機的話好似會有d bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/154401_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F154401_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=f98b8859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得留底一個聯絡到你嘅聯絡方式,等我地都搵到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/154426_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F154426_6bade8110601de30c47dd51084ffc663.JPG&h=8539286f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用TG登入嘅巴絲打,logout 只要係tg到按翻disconnect 就可以了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/155719_f349897532210e6ede7396e6a3015c67.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F155719_f349897532210e6ede7396e6a3015c67.jpeg&h=ecc08540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nuser 資料絕對唔會外洩,就算係admin 都唔會知道大家d私人資料,所以可以放心<br />\n今次要每人收翻$10因為我地都想繼續run 個網,比多d活動大家玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞手只求打個和,希望大家唔好見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2871536f649625d28ef2995aee2d1d3afaf0ec8","tid":782923,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"比100蚊可唔可以單對單教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6795ffe4db2fc2d7df7883b8b6c0e63e9cf8b61a","tid":782923,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2871536f649625d28ef2995aee2d1d3afaf0ec8","tid":782923,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"比100蚊可唔可以單對單教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"可以啊, 你留TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505439d0b10514da1d22da3f62f3888f503f3aa9","tid":782923,"uid":54142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老餅可唔可以來"},{"pid":"a9399c14480528b5967c1c45c43a39c3f38fc690","tid":782923,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505439d0b10514da1d22da3f62f3888f503f3aa9","tid":782923,"uid":54142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老餅可唔可以來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"可以照報住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb90